name: Nameless Project 1
description:
A game put together in a week for the /agdg/ jam.
The point was to challenge myself into being productive, and learn some new stuff. Both of which were a success.
I don't know if I'll be updating this project, starting on a new one, or what.

Hopefully this game can serve as an inspiration for someone.
And without further ado- I hope the .exe works, hope it doesn't crash, and give me 1,000,000 $.
